finished_channels.project-courtbot: T:Courtbot (https://court.bot/) is a text-message app that helps keep you updated with your court cases. After cases are booked, clients can text their case number to (844) 329-6801 to receive automatic reminders of court dates.D:Failure-to-appear and failure-to-pay fines can quickly snowball, especially for those living paycheck-to-paycheck. CourtBot helps clients avoid mistakes that burden them and the criminal justice system. Let's implement Courtbot nationwide!
